     C* E2: F-spec col 18 sequence (D = descending). Primary MDPRIM
     C* keys 3,2,1 (descending) vals 30,20,10; secondary MDSEC key
     C* 2 val 5. Correct descending-aware selection must pick the
     C* running MAXIMUM key each cycle and still detect the key=2
     C* match between files (MR). RPGRET = 30+20+10+5+1 = 66; a
     C* wrong ascending-assuming comparator desyncs the match and
     C* yields 65 (no MR) instead.
     FMDPRIM  IP DF    80              DISK
     FMDSEC   IS DF    80              DISK
     IMDPRIM      01
     I                                        1   20KEY     M1
     I                                        3   40VAL
     IMDSEC       02
     I                                        1   20SKEY    M1
     I                                        3   40SVAL
     C  01                 ADD  VAL       RPGRET
     C  02                 ADD  SVAL      RPGRET
     C  MR                 ADD  1         RPGRET
     CLR                   SETOF
